{
  "stem": "1965.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 355.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "See, they had these quotas all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was seven.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this, the only child that they took away from Landen, Belgium, that night was the only non-Jewish child, the same boy who had molested me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What a coincidence.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I felt bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't deserve that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If he were alive today I would hug him, because I understand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I understand, and I understood that sometimes we do things out of need, out of wanting to be loved, and most of all, for survival.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is also in Landen where one night the bombs were dropping very heavy, and right next to us was a big house too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That burned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all around the building where us Jewish children we're staying, all around, there was fire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's almost like a burning inferno, and we stood there like a bush that never got touched.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If God doesn't play miracles, he played there a miracle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Believe me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we survived Landen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In Landen I got horrific rashes, all again from tension and nerves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had to tie my hands and sweaters, so I would not scratch myself to bleeding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had whooping cough there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was always sick during the war from the fear-- that fear, that constant fear-- and lack of food-- starvings, eating very meager, meagerly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You cannot have the proper nutrition during war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So you eat whatever is possible to get on the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Madame Rothschild always tried to see that we had something decent in our stomach so we could survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But then we got note again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We must run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Gestapos are again behind Madame Rothschild and her children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we all, in the middle of the night-- that was so traumatic-- we all clothed ourselves fast.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
